South Africa's trade surplus fell sharply 940.8 mln rand March rise 1.62 billion February Customs Excise figure show. In February surplus stood 752.8 mln rand. Exports fell 3.24 mln rand March 3.36 billion February import rise 2.30 billion rand 1.74 billion. This brought total export quarter 9.92 billion rand import 6.45 billion rand surplus 3.47 billion versus 2.47 billion rand 1986 period. REUTER 